Liono awakens goes on his intercom "All maximals return to base lets put the 
newcomers through the streets." Ends his transmission. Looks at Zardus 
"Thanks for the help."  Liono suddenly drops to one knee "she is danger" 
Staggers to his feet " she can't leave not this soon. No, I will not cannot 
lose her twice." Liono races of towards the maximal base charging his arm 
cannon letting the power build. Arriving at the ark seeing Hades shot heading 
for Key's backside. Liono flies by grabbing Key and Spinning back so that he 
gets shot in the back by Hades his back metal smoldering as smoke is rising 
as Liono sets key down  "Hey Key we are a Team now and forever so don't you 
dare get killed on me." Liono sets her down growls in pain lowly "and 
whispers I love you key" Liono turns to face Shuko "This is between you and 
me lets see your the mighty Shuko I seen sewer Repair that look tougher and 
smell better." Liono Fires A nice sized blue clear past Shuko.
